No matter the cost?
Increase the transparency
Total data loss

The memory grows dim
Of wanting sensation
You tried a phantom limb
Hallucination

I know that you are there
I see you on my sleeve
An internal error
Ghost in the machine

All that we feel
Is virtually real
What will survive...
In real life, in real life?